Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, 10 years ago, in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where can freedom be found? \NA Sad Departure of a Boy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you sea cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are pretty serious \Nwounds, Luffy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Sabo anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo went home. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the boss monkey from Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the mountain bandit - Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why but I'm registered \Nas their foster parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stand by and watch someone \Ntry to take my boys' lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I'm not their real parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just let you go if you back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll have \Nto resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Ace?! \NDon't try to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam is a real villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a guy that a kid like you can beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--L-Let me fight, too!\N--No, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all, why don't you \Ntake Luffy and go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility \Nfor bringing Ace home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Y-Yes, ma'am!\N--Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Come home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you overestimate your \Nability, you'll only get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the strong and the \Ncowardly survive in wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave always die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dead man! The fire \Nis all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen all of the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's hot! It's hot!\N--There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The explosion left a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going \Non but this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, there is a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This path leads up to the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get away by following it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go before the fire returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful they are to burn the \Narea and the residents there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how did you know the situation in such \Nan outlying country in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something special \Nabout this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is an example of how \Nthe world will be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no happiness in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhere the undesirables are thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in a country like \Nthis, there are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who are willing to \Nfight for freedom, come aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:38.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GOA KINGDOM "ROYAL PALACE"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:44.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,HIGH TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called in the military. \NThey'll find him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sabo is giving us \Na hard time, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this town really safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the fire will \Nengulf the town any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way to enter High Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even allow a bug \Nto enter - nobles only!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Dadan didn't return \Nfrom the burning Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, wait, Luffy. You're not \Nrecovered - where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go and look for Ace and Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously wounded. You \Nhave to rest nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of troops \Nin the Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of the mess after the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just burned junk \Nthat they're throing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but survivors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna kill you if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Sabo is worrying about us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FORMER SITE OF THE GRAY TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great view!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain in the butt \Nto clean up this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we find a survivor, we're \Nto shoot them on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there aren't as many dead \Nbodies as I thought there'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a big fire. It could've \Nburned out the bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nervous yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that the \Nfire might get to this side of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Bluejam's \Nship was on fire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to know that \Nthose villains got burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! it's a nice day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is a lovely morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with this game of tag, okay boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you \Nrun, you can't get away, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the police and troops \Nhave a picture of you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never get out of High Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even out of this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, change your uniforms and \Nstart working here as guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have our duties...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that a nobleman can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the approval of your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, you must barricade \Nyourself in your room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and educate yourself in your role as a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, I can make things \Nhappen just by giving the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can take care of \Nyou or those two easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you mend your ways \Nand study hard like Stelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...study so that you can make your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who brought you into the world, happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that will make you happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dependable, Stelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Let me buy you some luxurious clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the ceremony the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, we'll see the \NCelestial Dragon in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check your homework tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that you died in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are okay, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:17:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I'll put you guys in \Ndanger if I try to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is like a birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can stand living in \Nthis country filled with stale air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shift is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be sleeping on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. By the way, how \Nare things in the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony is just a day away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy. People are going \Nwild getting ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime \Nthing but I got to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy and I will be the only \Ntwo in this house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the citizens will be \Nat the harbor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be such a pain to stand guard there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,compared with this baby-sitting gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day of the World Noble \Nfrom the Grand Line's visit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Goa Kingdom has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lavish ceremony is prepared \Nfor the arrival of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, \Nring, ring... Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is A-team on the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragon's ship \Nwill arrive in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. It's all quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue to stand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! There is a ship leaving port!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Is it a fishing boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back here! Don't get \Nin the way of the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a child! There's a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child? I wonder which family he's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible! The \Nguard is looking after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice day! It's \Nperfect for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That's mine! Somebody \Nstole my fish boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He has a black flag on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he think that he's a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! A kid can't just become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is he heading?\N--He's disrupting the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's ship will arrive soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, come back here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scariest fate for me is to \Nlose myself in this country and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turn into someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Sabo on that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's ship is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die if I crash into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. He's turning away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the commoners are welcoming us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so blessed that \Nit's rare to even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that a real \NCelestial Dragon is on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a fish boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice to be captain \Nof a ship like that someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing boat has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Dadan return to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As everyone is rejoicing \Nover their safe return,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they learn of the tragedy \Nthat struck Sabo at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing with sympathy \Nwhat Sabo had tried to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are befallen \Nby regret and grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take Good Care of Him! A \NLetter from the Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
